Then after a while I didn't think it was right but couldn't decide between LOAVES and fishes for a while and struggled with that section.

@Min - I'm pretty sure Dan is just mocking all the whiners and complainer who fill these threads later in the week because they believe anything they, personally, do not know right away is, by definition, "obscure" or in some other way unfair, simply because they' personally, did not already know it. They dismiss stuff they don't know as "trivia" -- and frankly, I consider ALL crossword entries to be in the trivia pigeonhole, and that ins one of the reasons I like crosswords -- because I also love trivia! 

Actually, I think you already know that and you're just giving Dan the kudos he so deserves. 

And here I am giving kudos to the both of you!

